# Account structure 

Within each service you can edit: 

* user permissions 
* email template to user
* accepted card types
* name that appears on the payment pages 
* accept 3DS (all the things you can manage on the settings page). 

Each service has its own API.

Within each you can edit: what appears on bank statement of your users, which
of your bank accounts your revenue goes to

